                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/722.]</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-11-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 26, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Congress this morning unanimously accepted resignation of President Victoria. The
                    Senate nominated the Archbishop by unanimous vote but must vote twice more on
                    the successive days. Same procedure necessary in the House. All political
                    prisoners have been released. McIntyre sailed today.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Russell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
